{"tid":2160344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：與林夕深情對話  恐家人淪中共人質 黎智英落淚（李八方）","createTime":"2020-08-17T01:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T01:21:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b431a1e6fc19146196f496f9866644db804b503c","tid":2160344,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T01:21:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200817/WDPP5FTXPBHZHFPIN2M6T3ZHP4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200817%2FWDPP5FTXPBHZHFPIN2M6T3ZHP4%2F&d=F9sYfJh4wRYjdPScc1OpRjUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=618b70cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200817%2FWDPP5FTXPBHZHFPIN2M6T3ZHP4%2F&h=e4b9f948\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200817/WDPP5FTXPBHZHFPIN2M6T3ZHP4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：與林夕深情對話 <br />\n恐家人淪中共人質 黎智英落淚（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/j3A5X0Ibs42M1PdRQdhFRqmuL2o=/1847x995/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/S5PJUIBPSFBZ7NKSPQD5VPPMNU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fj3A5X0Ibs42M1PdRQdhFRqmuL2o%3D%2F1847x995%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FS5PJUIBPSFBZ7NKSPQD5VPPMNU.jpg&h=85eefa26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「家人對我嚟講最重要，唔係事業唔係名譽，係家人，如果發生，我唔知點面對。」<br />\n<br />\n過去一星期香港傳媒同文化界迎來黑暗嘅時分，先有壹傳媒創辦人黎智英因國安法被捕，《蘋果》遭200名警察佔領搜查；後有填詞人林夕俾中央台點名批評佢為羅冠聰改歌詞，係同「港獨搞到一塊兒」。呢兩個俾北京打壓嘅人物，噚日喺《蘋果》果燃台隔空深情對話，兩個大男人除咗講政治講生活，仲傾到人生哲理同點克服恐懼，不過最感動嘅部份，就係黎智英講到屋企人，原本侃侃而談嘅佢，亦一度失控落淚無法說話。<br />\n<br />\n對談噚日下午開波，黎智英同夕爺都着上白色衫，兩人喺視像見面恍如隔世，平日叫黎智英做Jimmy嘅夕爺，噚日改口叫對方做肥佬黎，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Y6vOe_f8e91CK-3Q8L_LkGnWDsk=/1542x817/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FVO76VQG6VHEHGNZ7OJF7QLF7E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FY6vOe_f8e91CK-3Q8L_LkGnWDsk%3D%2F1542x817%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFVO76VQG6VHEHGNZ7OJF7QLF7E.jpg&h=32ceaaf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■與讀者談及兩子，黎智英感觸淚下：「家人對我嚟講最重要。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rSXT0ykOZpgWZWY6j3DCAoNLYRM=/1791x1011/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HTUFJHDAXFC5ROMSY3BSQ6JZOA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrSXT0ykOZpgWZWY6j3DCAoNLYRM%3D%2F1791x1011%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHTUFJHDAXFC5ROMSY3BSQ6JZOA.jpg&h=7d46dbb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■林夕哭着安慰黎智英：「未發生嘅事，放低憂慮。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KOb0stu4UH97GSEiZqSFuCwztEs=/1848x1035/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/G6ESJDO5FJBZFAV4OKJUXG3JFE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKOb0stu4UH97GSEiZqSFuCwztEs%3D%2F1848x1035%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FG6ESJDO5FJBZFAV4OKJUXG3JFE.jpg&h=f3c27d3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳小姐對於自己的問題觸動黎智英，說聲不好意思之餘，亦不禁落淚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夕爺︰放低憂慮<br />\n<br />\n兩人傾咗個幾小時，之後同讀者傾偈，其間一度冇聲，夕爺話唔通《蘋果》俾人滅聲？ 黎智英即刻話唔會，《蘋果》會遇到一啲阻滯係必然嘅，但會克服，《蘋果》會繼續發聲。<br />\n<br />\n咁打入嚟讀者講乜呢？。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另一位陳小姐提及黎智英兩個仔，。。。。。。。。。因此而得救。」<br />\n<br />\n夕爺仲勉勵香港人要同政權鬥長命，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"}]}